Ralph Byrd https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ralph_Byrd 0 Ralph Byrd (22 April 1909 – 18 August 1952) was an American actor. He was most famous for playing the comic strip character Dick Tracy on screen, in serials, movies and television. Ralph_Byrd ( 22_April_1909 – 18_August_1952 ) was an_American_actor .
